                               java.lang.String name)
        Find all elements within the current context using the given mechanism.
        Type Parameters:
        W - The sub WebElement type.
        Parameters:

      • findElement

        T findElement(org.openqa.selenium.By by,
              java.lang.String name)
        Find the first WebElement using the given method.
        Parameters:
        by - The locating mechanism.
        name - The name of the element.
        Returns:
        The first matching element on the current context.
        Throws:
        org.openqa.selenium.NoSuchElementException - If no matching elements are found.
